SMAC promotes the autoubiquitination and degradation of the IAP.

Varfolomeev E, Goncharov T, Fedorova AV, Dynek JN, Zobel K, Deshayes K, Fairbrother WJ, Vucic D. JBC 2008
pubmed: 18621737

Du, C. Cell 102, 33-42(2000).
Smac/DIABLO is released during MPT in the cytosol, where it inactivates caspase inhibitor XIAP

</comment>
      </annotation>
