pubmed: 18621737
Varfolomeev E, Goncharov T, Fedorova AV, Dynek JN, Zobel K, Deshayes K, Fairbrother WJ, Vucic D. JBC 2008

IAP is adding a lysine 63 ubiquitin on RIP1
Activation effect =&gt; subject of controversy
pubmed: 18621737
Varfolomeev E, Goncharov T, Fedorova AV, Dynek JN, Zobel K, Deshayes K, Fairbrother WJ, Vucic D. JBC 2008
</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="308" y="421" style=""/>
