    <annotation>
      <linklist>
        <link xlink:href="https://journals.plos.org/ploscompbiol/article?id=10.1371/journal.pcbi.1000702"/>
      </linklist>
      <comment>The model presented here is an update of the model of cell fate decision process published in 2010 (Calzone et al). 
- a feedback loop from NFkB to TNF was added
- new nodes representing the mRNA of some entities (or groups of proteins) have been added: mXIAP, mcIAP, and mROS.

For simulation of the population dynamics using UpPMaBoSS, we have added two extra node "DIVISION" and "DEATH".</comment>
    </annotation>
  </graph>
</gxl>
